title: The Kitchen at Jaipur Modern
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Italian, Organic, Mediterranean, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Modern and more upscale kind of place making Italian food from scratch, including the ketchup and guacamole sauce, using locally source and some organic vegetables. Has a falafel plate, fresh squeezed juice, sorbet, and a few other items that are or can be requested vegan - ask.
streetAddress: 51, Sardar Patel Rd, Dhuleshwar Garden, Hathroi
